        <title>重定向与转发的区别-202207171621</title>
        <link>https://news-epoch.github.io/p/%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E4%B8%8E%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB-202207171621/</link>
